Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.51,0:00:06.12,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,It was a story of two queens.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.45,0:00:11.12,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,It was a story of death and rebirth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.83,0:00:14.44,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,It was the sad tale about these
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.44,0:00:17.25,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,strange flags and the \Nheroes involved with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.83,0:00:20.71,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,There was once a peaceful country that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.71,0:00:22.55,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,two beautiful princesses ruled.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.72,0:00:26.22,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,But the country was
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.22,0:00:28.71,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,plunged into darkness by demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.82,0:00:32.35,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,The goddess in heaven was \Ntainted by the darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.35,0:00:35.49,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,and she entrusted her power \Nto a boy who was soon to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.89,0:00:39.25,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,She altered his appearance, \Nchanging him into a single flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.86,0:00:43.76,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,It was the Royal Flag that was to \Nchange the fate of the kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.28,0:00:46.44,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,The light which would \Ndrive away the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.85,0:00:49.64,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,To drive away the despair
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.64,0:00:51.78,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,that threatened the kingdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.78,0:00:54.18,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,the princesses and heroes fought...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.71,0:00:55.45,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,But
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.14,0:00:59.15,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,the knight, magician,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.15,0:01:02.39,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,bishop, and ninja lost their \Nlives at the first gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.43,0:01:05.02,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,At the second gate,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.02,0:01:07.66,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,the samurai fell victim to a \Ncurse while protecting the flag,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.66,0:01:10.14,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,and lost all of her memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.44,0:01:14.73,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,At the third gate, due \Nto the demon's schemes,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.03,0:01:17.68,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,the queen was separated from the heroes,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.03,0:01:20.77,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,took the flag, and tried to escape...
