Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.77,0:03:03.30,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,What is this, this here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.78,0:03:05.16,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It's popcorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.60,0:03:11.39,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,It's exploding...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.39,0:03:14.54,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe the common people \Nrisk their lives to make snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.41,0:03:17.79,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure several people have died just
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.79,0:03:20.65,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,to figure out how to make this treat,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.65,0:03:21.33,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,they have!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.33,0:03:23.93,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.30,0:03:29.74,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,So how long will it take \Nto get to the castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.74,0:03:31.12,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.12,0:03:34.94,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Things were pretty crazy. I'm \Nsure they'll be coming to get us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.62,0:03:38.69,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say this to anyone else, but the \NMajesty doesn't have much time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.71,0:03:41.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I might not matter,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.57,0:03:43.15,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm sure they'll do something
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.15,0:03:46.31,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,to make sure Hakua gets there in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.84,0:03:48.63,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,The guys from The Council of \Nthe Seven Virtues will, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.24,0:03:52.87,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What... did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.94,0:04:01.76,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with these guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.76,0:04:03.06,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.36,0:04:04.82,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,They're from the Council \Nof the Seven Virtues.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.17,0:04:17.81,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,The crown prince has ordered \Nme to bring you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.11,0:04:18.92,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.50,0:04:21.78,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,The Council of the Seven Virtues \Nis a special organization
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:24.17,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,that rules over the populace, \Nalong with the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.62,0:04:28.49,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,They're protectors of the Bladefield, \Nfounded along with the country itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.90,0:04:32.56,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,The Council of the Seven Virtues... \NMei worked with them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.29,0:04:35.00,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Why are they in this country?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:46.84,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Wow. It's a real castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:49.81,Kanojo_Flag_Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Souta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.31,0:04:54.84,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.84,0:04:56.52,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Okiku-nee.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.95,0:04:58.88,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,I heard what happened from Ruri.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:05:01.61,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry us so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:03.07,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.41,0:05:06.75,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,We weren't sure what to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.75,0:05:08.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Mei-oneechan helped us
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.50,0:05:11.26,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,contact the people at the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.26,0:05:13.58,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,She was really helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.85,0:05:17.58,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I-I wasn't really worried \Nabout Hatate Souta at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.82,0:05:21.42,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm glad you're all right, Souta-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.81,0:05:23.14,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.14,0:05:26.93,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Nanami, Hakua and I are all fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.91,0:05:30.85,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Hakua... You mean her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.85,0:05:31.52,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.88,0:05:37.24,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,A-Aren't you getting a little too \Nclose to the princess there,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.24,0:05:38.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Hatate Souta?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.13,0:05:40.48,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.04,0:05:43.65,Kanojo_Flag_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami, Hakua.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.49,0:05:46.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,B-Brother Elia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.80,0:05:48.24,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,Crown Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.55,0:05:50.23,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Elia,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're all right,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.23,0:05:52.23,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Elia,0000,0000,0000,,my lovely princesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.88,0:05:55.13,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Elia,0000,0000,0000,,You're Hatate Souta-kun, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.94,0:05:58.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Elia,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for helping them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.90,0:06:00.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no. Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:02.67,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,This is our brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.67,0:06:04.62,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,The Crown Prince, Elia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.00,0:06:07.76,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,He's a nice person that cares for us,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:10.18,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,even when our father doesn't \Nseem to pay us much attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.63,0:06:15.89,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,Number Seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.84,0:06:18.53,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Number Seven?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.89,0:06:21.65,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you're not mistaking \Nme for someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.10,0:06:27.11,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,So you don't remember me, Number Zero?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.41,0:06:31.01,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Have we met somewhere before?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.21,0:06:34.14,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.52,0:06:36.15,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you're not the right person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.63,0:06:43.71,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Elia,0000,0000,0000,,You done?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.99,0:06:44.78,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.51,0:06:47.94,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,All the opposition forces have been subdued.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.65,0:06:50.97,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,Now your rule is secure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.63,0:06:53.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Elia,0000,0000,0000,,Is that supposed to mean something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.68,0:06:57.52,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Elia,0000,0000,0000,,You let the opposition forces \Nknow about those two,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.82,0:06:59.98,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Elia,0000,0000,0000,,and baited them into that \Nassassination attempt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.98,0:07:01.81,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Elia,0000,0000,0000,,And the mere moment they failed,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:04.23,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Elia,0000,0000,0000,,you cast them aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.97,0:07:08.51,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,You are the sharpest among \Nthe kings we have seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.81,0:07:12.13,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,However, we cannot have \Nyour heir be a common fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.63,0:07:15.03,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,I merely tested them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:17.79,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Elia,0000,0000,0000,,And if something
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.22,0:07:20.41,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Elia,0000,0000,0000,,happened to them...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.70,0:07:24.46,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,We only need to create new heirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.76,0:07:26.49,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,But do not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.87,0:07:28.99,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,The heavenly destiny they carry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.08,0:07:32.93,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,They may even be the fated rulers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.22,0:07:35.09,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Elia,0000,0000,0000,,And you're saying that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.09,0:07:37.43,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Elia,0000,0000,0000,,this is how you've been \Nprotecting this country?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.93,0:07:40.21,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,It is the mission of the \NCouncil of the Seven Virtues
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.51,0:07:43.94,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,to watch over the world, my new King.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.02,0:07:52.03,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Elia,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.53,0:07:53.73,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Elia,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.80,0:07:55.70,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Why
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.57,0:08:00.08,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,is everyone collecting in my room when \Nwe've come all the way to Bladefield?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.36,0:08:03.90,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,This is my first time watching television, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.90,0:08:06.59,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Did they really keep you that sheltered?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.90,0:08:10.11,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.11,0:08:11.67,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,What type of press conference is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.67,0:08:13.93,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Elia,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}My beloved citizens.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.66,0:08:17.45,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Elia,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}My father, who has been bedridden \Nfor the past few days,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.45,0:08:19.62,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Elia,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Allbad Bladefield,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.17,0:08:22.43,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Elia,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}passed away this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.78,0:08:27.69,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Father had already passed away...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.26,0:08:31.02,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Elia,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}There is a reason this announcement \Nhas come to you all late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.02,0:08:34.31,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Elia,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}As soon as my father passed away, \Nthe second crown prince and
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.31,0:08:36.48,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Elia,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}the other princes below him, in other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.48,0:08:39.16,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Elia,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}my brothers, plotted to capture the crown,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.92,0:08:42.54,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Elia,0000,0000,0000,,and were subdued.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:46.72,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Elia,0000,0000,0000,,In order to corner me into submission,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.72,0:08:49.38,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Elia,0000,0000,0000,,they attempted to assassinate the thirteenth \Nand fourteenth crown princesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:52.97,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Elia,0000,0000,0000,,Fortunately, with help from \Ngood men, they were stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.66,0:08:55.68,Kanojo_Flag_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait, your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.11,0:08:57.82,Kanojo_Flag_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,If they were trying to obtain \Nthe crown for themselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.82,0:09:00.11,Kanojo_Flag_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,why would they attack the princesses with
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.11,0:09:02.18,Kanojo_Flag_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,the least right to inherit the throne?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:04.88,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Elia,0000,0000,0000,,That is because the thirteenth and
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.88,0:09:07.94,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Elia,0000,0000,0000,,fourteenth have a secret \Nregarding their birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.94,0:09:11.12,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,A secret regarding our birth?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.67,0:09:15.49,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Elia,0000,0000,0000,,In actuality, their father is not
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.85,0:09:17.11,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Elia,0000,0000,0000,,Allbad Bladefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.13,0:09:21.20,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Elia,0000,0000,0000,,I am their true father.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.26,0:09:28.71,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Elia,0000,0000,0000,,They are my successors.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.50,0:09:50.11,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to have you all come, \Nand then have this happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.48,0:09:53.23,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You don't have to worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.10,0:09:56.82,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,My friend's fathers are just like my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.69,0:10:00.61,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,So does that make us princesses, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.61,0:10:01.95,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Princesses?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.95,0:10:03.79,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Souta's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.16,0:10:06.22,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like we're talking \Nabout something else now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:10.22,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess it wasn't my \Nfather, but my grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.69,0:10:12.59,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,After a three-day mourning period,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:15.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,along with the coronation of the new king,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.00,0:10:17.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,the town will have a celebration.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.90,0:10:21.68,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,At least try to have some \Nfun there, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.72,0:10:32.61,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,She was really cared for,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.91,0:10:35.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,so I guess she still hasn't worked \Nout her feelings because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.51,0:10:38.03,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Nanami?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.33,0:10:39.86,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You don't seem too chipper yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.18,0:10:41.58,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.88,0:10:45.13,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I keep telling you I wasn't that close to—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.13,0:10:48.12,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You're upset that you aren't as \Nupset as you thought you'd be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.23,0:10:52.32,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry about \Nthinking you're so emotionless.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.72,0:10:55.84,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,The fact you're worried about that \Nright now is proof that you aren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.29,0:11:02.34,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You sure understand what people are thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.06,0:11:05.17,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Some people are good at analyzing \Nothers, especially you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.53,0:11:08.23,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Except I still can't see \Nanything with you, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.51,0:11:14.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Long live the Bladefield kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.00,0:11:16.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers to his highness, Elia!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:17.92,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,This is wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.92,0:11:20.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost like I'm in a fantasy book!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.57,0:11:22.82,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,It's like we're in a land of dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.14,0:11:25.78,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,This is good, Onee-sama, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.78,0:11:28.08,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Pay before you start eating!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.86,0:11:33.68,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad Hakua seems happier now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.16,0:11:35.77,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.81,0:11:37.96,Kanojo_Flag_Main,SA,0000,0000,0000,,We finally found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.25,0:11:40.64,Kanojo_Flag_Main,SA,0000,0000,0000,,You can't just stand around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.64,0:11:42.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,SB,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up. You're almost on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.36,0:11:46.53,Kanojo_Flag_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:50.52,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.15,0:11:53.41,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that they've mistaken you for
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.41,0:11:55.15,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,the people who were supposed \Nto be in an event.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.15,0:11:56.77,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,I would expect nothing less, Souta-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.77,0:11:59.03,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,S-Souta-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.67,0:12:00.61,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.26,0:12:04.99,Kanojo_Flag_Main,RA,0000,0000,0000,,The bride in the parade was beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.99,0:12:07.62,Kanojo_Flag_Main,RB,0000,0000,0000,,It's my first time seeing someone so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.84,0:12:09.59,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,They said there's a bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.59,0:12:11.17,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,How romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.17,0:12:13.12,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,How about we go take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.25,0:12:17.25,flag_12:13,,0000,0000,0000,,Conquest Complete
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.46,0:12:14.63,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.93,0:12:17.25,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,I might want to get married myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.07,0:12:27.64,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Everyone,0000,0000,0000,,M-M-Megu-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.14,0:12:35.91,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.93,0:12:38.42,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone saw me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.42,0:12:41.44,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be a beautiful bride now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.44,0:12:43.82,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,All,0000,0000,0000,,You wanted to be a bride?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.82,0:12:47.32,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. We can just get \NSouta-kun to marry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:49.99,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be a bride. I need to be a groom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.50,0:12:52.69,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,It's my first time being \Nin a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.99,0:12:56.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,Festivals are such fun, they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.24,0:12:58.05,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.35,0:12:59.75,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You sure you're not pushing yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.20,0:13:01.01,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.83,0:13:07.51,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,You were able to tell, you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:10.36,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I just kinda got the feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.78,0:13:13.34,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,Souta-san, u-um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.34,0:13:16.48,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,Could we talk for a little bit, could we?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:16.90,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.32,0:13:19.58,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be accustomed to trouble,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.58,0:13:22.74,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,so I figured you'd be good \Nfor some advice, you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.21,0:13:26.12,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Do I really seem that gloomy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.12,0:13:28.16,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,No, not just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.43,0:13:35.41,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,I... believe I have a \Nconnection to you, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.69,0:13:37.89,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,This flag...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.19,0:13:40.92,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I think Nanami would be better to talk to...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.92,0:13:44.66,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,No, it has to be you, it does!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.14,0:13:46.15,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.50,0:13:48.11,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It's the annoying girl flag...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.43,0:13:52.43,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,When we first met, you saved me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.43,0:13:55.77,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'll be able to help \Nme with everything, you will!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:13:57.10,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,She trusts me too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:14:01.19,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,I figured I could trust you with anything, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.19,0:14:02.78,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,She's jumping to extremes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.15,0:14:04.64,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,We're friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.64,0:14:07.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,Friends that can talk \Nabout anything, right, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.57,0:14:09.91,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like she can't live without me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.77,0:14:13.13,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,So what did you want to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.48,0:14:15.63,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,My father...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.00,0:14:18.95,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, my grandfather passed away, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.75,0:14:22.09,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,He treated me with a lot of affection.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.77,0:14:27.38,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,I imagine everyone is carrying \Nsome pain due to his death,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.38,0:14:30.84,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,but when I see everyone acting \Nas if they've forgotten him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.18,0:14:34.33,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,This might seem a little heartless,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.25,0:14:37.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,but I believe it's best for people to go about
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.83,0:14:40.52,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,their daily lives and not \Nstop because of the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:44.78,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure your grandfather \Nwould rather see you smile,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.95,0:14:48.28,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,than be sad and depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.17,0:14:50.44,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,Souta-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.11,0:14:53.03,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.24,0:14:55.52,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Hakua-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.52,0:14:57.43,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.43,0:15:01.71,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't notice you felt that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.71,0:15:03.90,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,And then we dragged you out here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.33,0:15:05.30,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:07.12,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.12,0:15:11.05,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very happy you're so \Nconcerned about me, I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.05,0:15:12.85,Kanojo_Flag_Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Hakua-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.10,0:15:14.76,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.65,0:15:19.52,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad that everyone who \Nloves Sou-kun has gotten closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:21.96,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm a member, too, am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.96,0:15:22.86,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.86,0:15:25.40,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you have feelings for Souta!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.62,0:15:28.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,This is what it means to \Nhave a close friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.00,0:15:29.89,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,Would you all like to give a cheer?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.89,0:15:31.03,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,Yes or no?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.03,0:15:32.53,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.53,0:15:35.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Hooray! Hooray! Souta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.50,0:15:38.30,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}You can do it, Souta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.30,0:15:40.94,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}You can do it, Souta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.79,0:15:41.92,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Why are they cheering for me and not Hakua?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.30,0:15:44.39,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for helping Hakua.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.43,0:15:47.64,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't really do anything on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.54,0:15:54.18,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we're headed back to Japan tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.94,0:15:57.23,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,A lot happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.23,0:15:58.93,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,but I guess it was a fun summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.16,0:16:17.13,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.92,0:16:21.41,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,Are you interested in that inscription?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.20,0:16:25.34,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.71,0:16:27.69,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I haven't told you my name, yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.14,0:16:29.82,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,I am Number Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.12,0:16:31.92,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Number Zero...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:33.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Number Seven,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.11,0:16:36.93,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Daimyouzamurai Mei's, former superior.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.93,0:16:37.93,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.66,0:16:40.58,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,This inscription is a fairy tale,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.88,0:16:45.55,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,told in the lands from which \NBladefield's founding queen hailed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.25,0:16:47.44,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,A fairy tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.62,0:16:51.10,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,It was the tale of two queens.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.03,0:16:55.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,As the heroes fell, one by one,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.80,0:16:57.75,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,a royal flag was raised aloft by
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.75,0:17:00.37,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,the last survivor, a golden haired princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:02.82,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,The demons fled,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.82,0:17:04.96,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,and the kingdom regained the light,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.22,0:17:08.96,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,but with the last arrow fired by the demons,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.36,0:17:11.51,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,the princess lost her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.20,0:17:15.86,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,The boy of the flag had received \Na blessing from the goddess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.29,0:17:17.85,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,But the boy used that blessing
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.85,0:17:21.17,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,to revive the princess and
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.17,0:17:23.90,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,the others instead of \Nhealing his own illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.48,0:17:27.96,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,He remained in the shape of the royal \Nflag, never to return to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.96,0:17:31.96,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,The princesses and her comrades made this
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.96,0:17:34.40,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,torn flag the symbol of the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.57,0:17:38.18,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,It is the story of a boy with no name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.02,0:17:43.41,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,It is the story of hope and despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.78,0:17:47.67,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,It is the tragic story of a young man,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.67,0:17:50.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,the hero who turned into a strange \Nflag and saved a country.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.01,0:17:52.02,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.53,0:17:56.87,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It matches up too closely with my past...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.54,0:18:08.14,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,If this fairy tale is a \Nmetaphor for my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.26,0:18:11.11,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,then that means I will only meet
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.24,0:18:15.44,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,...destruction...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.58,0:18:21.39,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Is everything I do pointless?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.87,0:18:25.12,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Is the light I've finally found meaningless?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.11,0:18:28.33,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,What is the world to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.15,0:18:31.34,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.03,0:18:33.92,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a symbol of hatred?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.66,0:18:35.59,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,Or do you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.09,0:18:39.75,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,love it so much you'd sacrifice \Nanything to protect it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.90,0:18:44.71,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I... The world...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.02,0:18:48.03,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It won't go away...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.74,0:18:51.89,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I've triggered every flag I can think \Nof that can get around a death flag!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.55,0:18:54.41,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,But it still won't go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.12,0:18:56.79,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It won't go away! It won't go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.79,0:18:58.01,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It won't go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.74,0:19:03.03,Kanojo_Flag_Main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Are you embarrassed that you \Nwere the only one who survived?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.08,0:19:06.21,Kanojo_Flag_Main,V,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who killed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.21,0:19:08.46,Kanojo_Flag_Main,V2,0000,0000,0000,,Give them back! You murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.76,0:19:09.60,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.30,0:19:14.21,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,the death flag is gathering everyone's \Nanger and trying to kill me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.53,0:19:15.25,Kanojo_Flag_Main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.54,0:19:17.97,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,No one really wants that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.97,0:19:18.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:20.76,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,No. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.99,0:19:22.64,Kanojo_Flag_Main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Die. Die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.64,0:19:24.14,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,No. No. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.14,0:19:27.52,Kanojo_Flag_Main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Die. Die. Die. Die. Die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.71,0:19:29.37,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.86,0:19:34.77,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take it with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.36,0:19:38.73,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take the hatred caused by this flag...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.99,0:19:41.38,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,This world...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.30,0:19:44.25,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.86,0:20:04.99,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,I love the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.29,0:20:09.56,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,I would easily kill a single \Nprincess for the sake of world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.31,0:20:12.06,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.41,0:20:16.23,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I was behind that assassination attempt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.18,0:20:20.04,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see how capable the \Nsucceeding princesses would be,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.04,0:20:22.07,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,and get rid of the opposition \Nin one fell swoop.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.56,0:20:24.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty good plan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.39,0:20:26.33,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.33,0:20:27.25,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,Of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.60,0:20:30.33,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,I would give my life if necessary, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.64,0:20:31.75,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,She's serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.72,0:20:35.08,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,For the world, she'd...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.74,0:20:39.34,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,I shall ask you once more. How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.16,0:20:42.84,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,About the world that didn't need you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.54,0:20:45.53,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.54,0:20:47.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.56,0:20:51.60,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,Let us meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.88,0:20:56.23,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,I would be happy to
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.52,0:20:57.48,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,hear your answer then.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.01,0:22:52.74,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,I shall praise you for
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.74,0:22:55.81,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,deceiving us and escaping from your bonds.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.33,0:22:58.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,However, it is pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.37,0:23:01.78,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,Someone like you will never be able to save
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.23,0:23:03.68,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,Hatate Souta.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.44,0:23:07.49,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,Save my beloved brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.13,0:23:12.44,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,Roar! Gawo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.44,0:23:14.86,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Have you done the preview before, Hakua?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.86,0:23:16.69,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a Bladefield princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.69,0:23:19.26,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,I can handle the preview with ease, I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.26,0:23:20.75,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.75,0:23:23.84,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,So what is it, this preview?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.84,0:23:25.85,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that flag was coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.85,0:23:29.18,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, next time I'll \Nstart studying in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.18,0:23:31.51,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it has much to \Ndo with this preview, I don't.
